   ssp. 
   mongolica
   , 
   H. r. 
   ssp. 
   turkestanica
   , 
   H. 
   gyantsensis, 
   H. Neurocarpa
   , 
   H. tibetana
   , were collected from natural resources locations in Tibet, Xinjiang, Qinghai, Gansu, to analyze the total flavonoids, total polyphenol, total polysaccharide and alkaloids of them, which showed that the total flavonoids and total polyphenol of 
