   H. r. 
   ssp. 
   turkestanica
   . Considering the artificial afforestation of Genus 
   Hippophae
    in China, the suggestions of leaves forests should be established from 
   H. r. 
   ssp. 
   mongolica
    in the Northeastern China, 
   H. r. 
   ssp. 
   mongolica
    and 
   H. r. 
   ssp. 
   turkestanica
    in Xinjiang, 
   Hippophae r. 
   ssp. 
   sinensis
    in the Loess Plateau, and 
   H. gyantsensis
    and
    H. r. 
   ssp. 
   turkestanica
    in Tibet, to get leaves for making tea and other functional products.
    
  
 
